      "content": "uugh that's scary. i'm just so tired of the hospital bills and the wait times. if i just take a couple of the oxy i have left and maybe some diclofenac on top of it, do you think that would be enough to numb the pain so i can just sleep until tomorrow morning? i'll just monitor it then.",
